1935;;The Girl in the Crowd;;British;;Michael Powell;;Patricia Hilliard, Googie Withers;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Girl_in_the_Crowd;;The wife of a bookseller gives advice about picking up woman to her husband's friend (whom she has never met) over the phone. She advises him simply to follow the first pretty woman he sees. Unfortunately, when he takes her advice, she is the girl in the crowd he ends up following, leading to his arrest.